# Destination host allowlist for the sandbox egress proxy.
# POSIX extended regex, matched against the request host (FilterExtended On,
# FilterURLs Off). With FilterDefaultDeny Yes, ONLY hosts matching a line
# here are permitted; everything else is refused. One pattern per line.
#
# Python package installs (pip / uv):
(^|\.)pypi\.org$
(^|\.)pythonhosted\.org$
# Node package installs (npm):
(^|\.)npmjs\.org$
# Git operations + release/asset downloads on GitHub:
(^|\.)github\.com$
(^|\.)githubusercontent\.com$
